title: Direction request change
caption: Comparison between 1 January, 2020 to 13 January, 2020 (baseline) and subsequent days' change in volume of direction requests in Austin TX.
insights: Between mid-March and mid-May, direction requests dropped by an average of -49%.
Eversince then, public transit direction requests have remained -27% below the baseline while walking and driving direction requests are 60% and 20% respectively above the baseline.
